import { Flex, Box, Text } from '@chakra-ui/react'

const heading = {
  fontSize: 48,
  fontWeight: 700,
  textAlign: 'left' as const,
  color: 'pale_dogwood',
  textShadow: '-2px 1px 2px #22223B',
  pl: '1%'
}

export default function Heading() {
  return (
    <Flex >
      <Box w='50%' className='name'>
        <Text {...heading} >Ari Wisenburn</Text>
      </Box>
      <Box flex='1'>
        <Text>Box 3</Text>
      </Box>
    </Flex >
  )
}
